data.text:
Post Vaccination Day 3 : Alhamdulillah so far no side effects since Day 1 😇 

Betul la cakap Doctor most of us akan rasa common symptoms macam pening, demam & sengal tangan tapi ade yang takde ape2 depends on antibody masing2.

Tips : Lepas ambik vaccine, please take your vitamin C.

Then before sleep minum Delima cider.
